rV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-L%C3%A3m/Qu%C3%A1-Y%C3%AAn-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh-than-T%E1%BA%A1i-Thanh-Ho%C3%A1-ph%E1%BB%A7-t%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n-th%E1%BB%9Di-t%C3%A1c/poem-xSJ2BEHm2Xav9pVkFSdbRA">Quá Yên Định than (Tại Thanh Hoá phủ tòng quân thời tác) - 過安定灘（在清化府從軍時作）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-L%C3%A3m/author-11a_esS_09VNjvlkNmasVQ">Vũ Lãm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cung-Do%C3%A3n/T%E1%BB%91ng-Khu%E1%BA%A5t-%C3%94ng-S%C6%A1n/poem-Z4qbnXyYpT8WKl5rq4nN1Q">Tống Khuất Ông Sơn - 送屈翁山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cung-Do%C3%A3n/author-8wX_f--qBGvseLM4iD_Z7A">Trần Cung Doãn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%B4ng-V%C5%A9-sinh-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-VDPbM6HbzyGfnLNl6bn0NQ">Tông Vũ sinh nhật - 宗武生日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
